  "texts": [
    "By evaluating the differences in STEM TPD across regions, this study sheds light on how regional efforts are essential in achieving the broader national STEM education objectives.",
    "Addressing the disparities in resource allocation and support for teacher development is critical for ensuring that all regions can contribute to the realization of China's national STEM education goals.",
    "Ensuring equitable access to high-quality STEM TPD across all regions is vital for achieving China's national STEM education objectives and crucial for maintaining global competitiveness in STEM fields.",
    "Countries with similar socio-economic and regional differences may find useful strategies in China's approach to professional development.",
    "By analyzing these programs, this study contributes to the global conversation on improving teacher efficacy, enhancing STEM teaching practices, and ultimately raising student outcomes in STEM disciplines."
